The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | King confirms
                                                   King confirms
                      
	New Delhi: Team India trainer Gregory Allen King has decided to quit after the ongoing tri-series in Australia, BCCI secretary Niranjan Shah confirmed on Friday. Physio John Gloster has already decided not to renew his contract.         
	[That King would follow in the footsteps of Gloster was reported by The Telegraph on Friday.]         
	Shah said King, who was contracted with the BCCI till December 2007, had decided against seeking an extension.           (PTI)                                                                                                                   
